1. *Svakih* pet minuta se čuje zvuk sirene. (Every five minutes, you can hear the sound of the siren.)
2. Ne želim da *svakih* par sati moram da punim bateriju. (I don't want to have to charge the battery every couple of hours.)
3. *Svakih* deset koraka bi trebalo da se odmoriš. (You should take a break every ten steps.)
4. Oni organizuju *svakih* godinu dana humanitarni koncert. (They organize a charity concert every year.)
5. *Svakih* nekoliko meseci mi stižu novi brojevi časopisa. (New issues of the magazine arrive every few months.)
6. Moramo da proveravamo temperaturu *svakih* nekoliko sati. (We need to check the temperature every few hours.)
7. *Svakih* sedam dana menjamo posteljinu. (We change the bedding every seven days.)
8. *Svakih* pet kilometara nalazi se odmorište. (There is a rest stop every five kilometers.)
9. *Svakih* petoro ljudi dobija nagradu. (Every group of five people receives a prize.)
10. *Svakih* nekoliko godina se pojavljuje nova verzija softvera. (A new version of the software is released every few years.)